A little suggestion for popcorn seasoning: I put kosher salt, nooch, truffle powder (or truffle salt), & garlic powder in a spice grinder and grind until fine. The finer the seasoning the better it sticks. Of course the seasonings can be switched up but the key is grinding the salt into, basically, a powder.
